---
title: "JavaScript30 by Chris Burnell"
lede: "Welcome to my attempt at this 30-day JavaScript challenge!"
color: "#5f8aa6"
---
<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head>
    <meta charset="utf-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0, minimal-ui">
    <title>{{ title }}</title>
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="https://chrisburnell.com/css/main.css">
    <link rel="icon" href="data:image/svg+xml,<svg xmlns=%22http://www.w3.org/2000/svg%22 viewBox=%220 0 100 100%22><text y=%22.9em%22 font-size=%2290%22>ðŸ—“</text></svg>">
    <meta name="apple-mobile-web-app-title" content="{{ title }}">
    <meta name="description" content="{{ lede }}">
    <meta name="theme-color" content="{{ color }}">
    <meta name="msapplication-navbutton-color" content="{{ color }}">
    <meta name="apple-mobile-web-app-status-bar-style" content="{{ color }}">
    <meta http-equiv="cleartype" content="on">
    <meta name="robots" content="noindex,nofollow">
</head>
<body>

    <a href="#content" class="[ hidden ]">Skip to main content</a>

    <header class="[ header ]">
        <div class="[ wrap wrap--large ]">
            <div class="[ logo ]" href="https://chrisburnell.com/" rel="home" title="Chris Burnell">
                <svg aria-hidden="true" class="[ icon icon--raven ]">
                    <use xlink:href="/images/sprites.svg#svg--raven"></use>
                </svg>
            </div>
            <nav class="[ navigation ]">
                <ol class="[ navigation__list ]">
                    <li>
                        <a href="https://chrisburnell.com/">My Homepage</a>
                    </li>
                </ol>
            </nav>
        </div>
    </header>

    <main class="main">
        <article id="content" class="[ content ] [ wrap ] [ page ]">
            <h1 id="title" class="[ title ]">{{ title }}</h1>
            <div class="[ details ]">
                <p>{{ lede }}</p>
            </div>
            <div class="[ content__body ]">
                <h2>The Challenges</h2>
                <nav class="[ deck ] [ h-feed ]">
                    {% for item in collections.challenges %}
                        <article class="[ h-entry ]">
                            <h3><a class="p-name" href="{{ item.url }}"><small>{{ loop.length - loop.index0 }}.</small> {{ item.data.title }}</a></h3>
                            {% if item.data.lede %}
                                <p class="p-summary">{{ item.data.lede | markdownFormat | safe }}</p>
                            {% endif %}
                            <div class="[ deck__meta ]">
                                <small>published</small>
                                <a class="[ u-url ]" href="{{ item.url }}" tabindex="-1">
                                    <time class="[ dt-published ]" datetime="{{ item.date | w3DateFormat }}">{{ item.date | dateFormat }}</time>
                                </a>
                            </div>
                        </article>
                    {% endfor %}
                </nav>
            </div>
            <div class="[ box ] [ meta ]">
                <p>Go to <a href="https://javascript30.com/">JavaScript30.com</a> for more details and to get started yourself!</p>
                <hr>
                <p>Pals also working through these challenges:</p>
                <ul class="[ meta__list ]">
                    <li><a href="https://github.com/hirusi/learn-js30">Ru Singh</a></li>
                </ul>
            </div>
        </article>
    </main>

    <footer class="[ footer ]">
        <div class="[ wrap ]">
            <div class=" [ author ] [ h-card  p-author ] ">
                <a class=" [ author__information ] [ u-url u-uid ] " href="https://chrisburnell.com/" rel="author  me">
                    <picture class=" [ author__image ] [ canada ] ">
                        <source srcset="/images/avatar.webp 1x,
                                        /images/avatar@2x.webp 2x,
                                        /images/avatar@3x.webp 3x,
                                        /images/avatar@4x.webp 4x"
                                type="image/webp" />
                        <img alt="Chris Burnell" class=" [ u-photo ] "
                            src="/images/avatar.jpg"
                            srcset="/images/avatar.jpg 1x,
                                    /images/avatar@2x.jpg 2x,
                                    /images/avatar@3x.jpg 3x,
                                    /images/avatar@4x.jpg 4x"
                            width="100" height="100">
                    </picture>
                    <div class=" [ author__name ] ">
                        <small>about</small>
                        <span class=" [ anchor ] [ canada ] [ p-name ] ">Chris Burnell</span>
                    </div>
                </a>
                <div class=" [ author__biography ] ">
                    <p class="[ p-note ]">Iâ€™m <span class="canada">Chris Burnell</span>, a <span class="canada">Canadian</span> <span class="p-job-title">Front End Developer</span>, <span class="p-role">Organiser</span> for <a href="https://stateofthebrowser.com"><span class="p-org">London Web Standards</span></a>, <a href="https://bloodbuilder.online/feonir">Elven Sorcerer</a>, and <a href="/projects">rabbit-hole deep-diver</a> living in <span class="p-locality">London, England</span>.</p>
                    <p><a href="https://github.com/chrisburnell/JavaScript30/tree/master/{{ page.inputPath }}">You can edit this page.</a></p>
                </div>
                <a class=" [ u-url ] " href="https://chrisburnell.com/about/" rel="author me" hidden> </a>
                <data class=" [ p-x-pronoun-nominative ] " value="he" hidden> </data>
                <data class=" [ p-x-pronoun-oblique ] " value="him" hidden> </data>
                <data class=" [ p-x-pronoun-possessive ] " value="his" hidden> </data>
            </div>
            <ol class="[ footer__navigation ]">
                <li>
                    <a id="copyright" href="https://chrisburnell.com/license/" rel="license">Â© 2020 <span class="[ canada ]">Chris Burnell</span></a>
                </li>
                <li>
                    <a href="https://github.com/chrisburnell" rel="me">GitHub</a>
                </li>
                <li>
                    <a href="https://twitter.com/iamchrisburnell" rel="me">Twitter</a>
                </li>
                <li>
                    <a href="https://codepen.io/chrisburnell" rel="me">CodePen</a>
                </li>
                <li>
                    <a href="https://chrisburnell.com/feed.xml" rel="me">RSS</a>
                </li>
            </ol>
        </div>
    </footer>

</body>
</html>
